  "prompt": "How do I file a complaint against Quora?",
  "response": "Here are a few ways to file a complaint or contact Quora:\n\n1. Direct Support Contact\n- Go to Quora's Help Center at help.quora.com\n- Click on \"Contact Us\" or \"Support\"\n- Submit a ticket describing your specific issue\n\n2. Email\n- Contact Quora Support at direct@quora.com\n\n3. Report Specific Issues On-Platform\n- For content violations, use the \"Report\" option next to the specific post or comment\n- For user behavior issues, you can report individual users directly on their profile\n\n4. Social Media Channels\n- Reach out via Quora's Twitter or Facebook support accounts\n\n5. Community Guidelines Violations\n- Review Quora's Community Guidelines and report violations through their designated reporting mechanisms\n\n6. Data Privacy or Legal Concerns\n- For serious issues, contact legal@quora.com\n\nTips:\n- Be specific and clear about your complaint\n- Provide relevant screenshots or details\n- Be professional and factual in your communication\n\nNote: The exact process might change, so always check their current support website for the most up-to-date contact methods.",
